Germany’s Von der Leyen Wants Euro-Debt Sanctions, FAZ Reports

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-09-21T06:19:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/germany-s-von-der-leyen-wants-euro-debt-sanctions-faz-reports.html
German Labor Minister Ursula von der Leyen said euro-area nations that breach debt rules should
face sanctions to protect the euro,  Frankfurter Allgemeine
Zeitung  reported today, citing an interview with the minister.  Von der Leyen also said that a central authority should
step in when countries don’t follow common rules or borrow too
much, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
